# notificationType

**Type**

A notification type value that App Store Server Notifications 2 uses.

## Declaration

```swift
string notificationType
```

## Discussion

For the list of notification types available in [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/AppStoreServerNotifications] version 2, see [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/AppStoreServerNotifications/notificationType].

## Data types

- **startDate**: The start date of a timespan, expressed in UNIX time, in milliseconds.
- **endDate**: The end date of a timespan, expressed in UNIX time, in milliseconds.
- **notificationSubtype**: A notification subtype value that App Store Server Notifications 2 uses.
- **onlyFailures**: A Boolean value that indicates whether the response includes only notifications that failed to reach your server.
